note right of Learner
  Any authenticated user
  can access learning platform
  via SSO from main platform
  
  Roles: Researcher, Organization,
  Staff, or dedicated learner
end note

note right of Instructor
  Platform administrators
  who create and manage
  learning content
end note

note bottom of UC8
  Isolated simulation environment
  - Separate database
  - Sandboxed containers
  - No production data
  - Safe for practice
end note

@enduml
